{"tid":706843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"揸500萬「狂牛」飆車 警截車拉人","createTime":"2018-06-18T08:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T15:21:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5a3dc401b23f3c2f327604f5a54d3c5ca32322de","tid":706843,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T08:34:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180618/20424148\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180618%2F20424148&d=zZOMUCSM1oidYsKv1u2NiZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=8962ec47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180618%2F20424148&h=a7002779\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180618/20424148</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月18日 <br />\n<br />\n揸500萬「狂牛」飆車<br />\n警截車拉人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】新界北總區交通部執行及管制組特遣隊人員，昨晨1時40分於元朗青山公路洪水橋段進行反超速巡邏，期間發現一輛黃色林寶堅尼超級跑車，沿青山公路往元朗方向飛馳，警員隨即展開追截，據稱現場路段時速限制70公里，跑車以時速180公里高速行駛。<br />\n<br />\n警車追至青山公路近水邊圍邨對開，終將跑車截停，姓李59歲司機涉嫌危險駕駛被捕，他已獲准保釋候查，須於8月上旬向警方報到。涉事超跑被扣查於大欖涌車輛檢驗中心作進一步檢驗。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲駕駛人士，切勿以身試法。警方會不時採取行動打擊車輛超速及非法改裝，以保障道路安全。據稱，涉事超跑是新車，落地不久，有「狂牛」之稱，車價約為500萬元。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n三父子同人嘈　中伏被電筒扑傷頭<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n男子西區墮海　蛙人救起送院亡"},{"pid":"0d83bd08b61a6647b0b97572591a092d1d6277ce","tid":706843,"uid":4739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:50:03.000Z","msg":"佢渣GTR佢洗比人拉"},{"pid":"5ac82d8f7a00b87583dd17e82cf0c99c0f91358d","tid":706843,"uid":83350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d83bd08b61a6647b0b97572591a092d1d6277ce","tid":706843,"uid":4739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:50:03.000Z","msg":"佢渣GTR佢洗比人拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T13:29:10.000Z","msg":"渣GTR 佢死左啦"},{"pid":"7ec2a9ab54866fcd4595c09b82e50c40fa0f4eaf","tid":706843,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T13:38:40.000Z","msg":"渣林寶都比人捉到 執柒左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb49e3552df8607e9a620164419c3dc326cc4d43","tid":706843,"uid":14073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T13:40:55.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  揸下車姐，跑車180咪同普通車80一樣"},{"pid":"8586a6b37e55b89044a23b46c836b5c91b34ffc7","tid":706843,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T13:48:56.000Z","msg":"跑車本來就應該要慢駛，咁先多人睇到，同埋眼紅。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ebdf1dd41aa177c23202f0d48235972e61ebae0","tid":706843,"uid":72735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ec2a9ab54866fcd4595c09b82e50c40fa0f4eaf","tid":706843,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T13:38:40.000Z","msg":"渣林寶都比人捉到 執柒左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T13:49:00.000Z","msg":"香港地揸咩46都走唔甩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fffcdc58355990911d8dd32b272b30074a0a1cfe","tid":706843,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T13:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連警車都截到, 即係是但搵個小巴司機都片得贏呢條友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eeac184f5bbe56ef2b578c2b655bb55d5743f68","tid":706843,"uid":8810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T13:55:11.000Z","msg":"59歲司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7111b1a89a056f8faed0045fc585c16aafe08bd7","tid":706843,"uid":119135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco